            {
                title: 'Its applications',
                article: [
                    "While calculus undeniably presents formidable challenges to learners, its relevance in various fields cannot be overstated. From unraveling the mysteries of the universe to driving technological advancements, calculus is a cornerstone of human knowledge and progress.",
                ],
            },
            {
                title: 'Foundations of Modern Science',
                article: [
                    "Calculus is the mathematical backbone of science and engineering. It provides the tools necessary for modeling and analyzing complex physical phenomena. Without calculus, many scientific breakthroughs, from understanding the motion of planets to designing advanced technologies, would be impossible."
                ],
            },
            {
                title: 'Technology and Innovation',
